      public java.util.List<java.lang.String> getPhonex()
      Gets the value of the phonex property.

      This accessor method returns a reference to the live list, not a snapshot. Therefore any modification you make to the returned list will be present inside the JAXB object. This is why there is not a set method for the phonex property.
